  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Take a reduced penalty to your AC against melee attacks while prone</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Base attack bonus +1.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>If you have been prone since the end of your last turn, the penalty to your Armor Class against melee attacks made against you is reduced to -2. In addition, the bonus to your Armor Class against ranged attacks made against you is increased to +6.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>As long as you have at least 1 stamina point in your stamina pool, you gain the bonuses from this feat even if you haven't been prone since the end of your last turn.",
